name: grid.js
description: Grid.js is a free and open-source HTML table plugin written in TypeScript. It works with most JavaScript frameworks, including React, Angular, Vue, and VanillaJs.

name: datatable.js
description: DataTables is an open-source jQuery plugin for enhancing an HTML table. Created by Allan Jardine under the MIT license.

name: react-table
description: React Table is a lightweight, extensible table library for React. It's designed to help you build simple or complex data tables in React quickly.
